item.title: Medals aplenty for the rowers
item.author: Tobias Heaton,
item.description: For Imperial’s rowers, BUCS Head was moved from the metropolitan Boston to the tropical Newcastle this year (a Head race is a rowing time trial, rather than a side by side race). ICBC sent up 22 of our finest athletes to compete on the Sunday, in an attempt to prove that the strength of our squad is …
